</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167793636568"><para id="fs-id1167793636569"><newline/>
<media id="fs-id1167793636573" alt="This figure is has two graphs. They are the equations 2y=x and y+y^3=x. The graphs intersect, forming two regions. The regions are shaded.">
